goals.2: Identify the BGP for Walt Disney Animation Studios
goals.3: Identify the BGP for Walt Disney (person)
goals.4: List all the films created by the Walt Disney Animation Studios while Walt Disney was alive (the result set must be a list of couples films IRI and label).
goals.5: Find the name of the voice actors who participated in more than 5 films by the Walt Disney Animation Studios (the result set must be a list of triples voice actors IRI, label and #films).
goals.6: Identify the BGP for the film "The Little Mermaid"
goals.7: Find who worked on both "The Little Mermaid" and "The Lion King" (the result set must be a list of couples worker IRI and label).
goals.8: Identify the BGP for Academy Awards
goals.9: For each films created by the Walt Disney Animation Studios return the number of nomination for an Academy Awards. Return only films with at least one nomination. (the result set must be triples of films IRI, label and #nomination).

startup the evaluation
setup the file and create the empty json
properties of The Lion King
1.query: SELECT DISTINCT ?p ?name WHERE { wd:Q36479 ?p ?obj . FILTER(!isLiteral(?obj)). ?p sc:name ?name. }
output: original language of film or TV show

1.query: SELECT DISTINCT ?obj ?name WHERE { wd:Q36479 wdt:P31 ?obj . ?obj sc:name ?name. }
SELECT DISTINCT ?obj ?name WHERE { wd:Q36479 wdt:P31/wdt:P279+ ?obj . ?obj sc:name ?name. }
SELECT DISTINCT ?inst ?name WHERE { BIND(wd:Q11424 AS ?inst). ?inst sc:name ?name. }

2.query: SELECT DISTINCT ?obj ?nO WHERE { wd:Q36479 ?p ?obj . FILTER(!isLiteral(?obj)). ?obj sc:name ?nO. FILTER(REGEX(?nO,"[D,d]isney")). ?p sc:name ?name. }

4.narrative: find date of birth of Walt Disney
4.query: SELECT DISTINCT ?prop ?name WHERE { wd:Q8704 ?prop ?obj . ?prop sc:name ?name. FILTER(REGEX(?name,"[D,d]ate")). }

4.narrative: filter for films publicated before the Walt Disney's death
4.query: SELECT DISTINCT ?film ?name WHERE { wd:Q8704 wdt:P570 ?death. ?film wdt:P272 wd:Q1047410 ; wdt:P577 ?publ. FILTER(?publ < ?death). ?film sc:name ?name. }

5.narrative: workers more present on the Walt Disney's films
5.query: SELECT ?va ?name COUNT(DISTINCT ?film) AS ?counts WHERE { ?film wdt:P272 wd:Q1047410 . ?film wdt:P725 ?va. ?va sc:name ?name. } GROUP BY ?va ?name HAVING (COUNT(DISTINCT ?film) > 5)

SELECT DISTINCT ?film ?name WHERE { wd:Q36479 ?p ?obj . FILTER(!isLiteral(?obj)). ?film wdt:P179 ?obj ; wdt:P31 ?inst. ?film sc:name ?name. ?inst sc:name ?iname. FILTER(REGEX(?name,"[L,l]ittle")). }
